ChangeItem.newstring: Security & permissions: How to control who can edit or or manage projects

[https://www.loom.com/embed/b387523478a3417da222bc69403db9c0?sid=9c5cd990-e88a-41ca-b1c7-4f5fbe8ceb31|https://www.loom.com/embed/b387523478a3417da222bc69403db9c0?sid=9c5cd990-e88a-41ca-b1c7-4f5fbe8ceb31|smart-embed]
In this video, well show you how to control who can create, edit, or change project settings in Jira. Learn how to customize permissions so the right people have the right access, so your projects are secure and organized.
*Resources:*
* [Permissions overview|https://www.atlassian.com/software/jira/guides/permissions/overview] * [How to change permissions|https://www.atlassian.com/software/jira/guides/permissions/tutorials] * [Manage project permissions|https://support.atlassian.com/jira-cloud-administration/docs/manage-project-permissions/]
Plans: How to use detailed roadmaps to plan out your work

[https://www.loom.com/embed/88f966bbfc434507b26c397ab0923f3e?sid=3db973df-3c55-4045-a363-12053db42c32|https://www.loom.com/embed/88f966bbfc434507b26c397ab0923f3e?sid=3db973df-3c55-4045-a363-12053db42c32|smart-embed]
In this video, well show you how to use Plans to plan your work, track dependencies, and keep teams aligned. Learn how to build roadmaps into your teams rituals and manage work so you always deliver on time.
*Resources:*
* [Plans overview|https://www.atlassian.com/software/jira/guides/advanced-roadmaps/overview] * [Getting started with Plans|https://support.atlassian.com/jira-software-cloud/docs/get-started-with-advanced-roadmaps/] * [More video tutorials on how to create a Plan|https://www.atlassian.com/software/jira/guides/advanced-roadmaps/tutorials]
Atlassian Intelligence: How to work smarter with AI

[https://www.loom.com/embed/7fa7364ac5814377bf339d2ce31ae2a5?sid=4e385c77-5ea4-4c1d-adda-ebc8b3b3c698|https://www.loom.com/embed/7fa7364ac5814377bf339d2ce31ae2a5?sid=4e385c77-5ea4-4c1d-adda-ebc8b3b3c698|smart-embed]

Issue.creator: 9ea987f4-57dd-49c9-b17d-0a433b7c525f
Issue.summary: Atlassian Intelligence: How to work smarter with AI
Issue.description:
[https://www.loom.com/embed/7fa7364ac5814377bf339d2ce31ae2a5?sid=4e385c77-5ea4-4c1d-adda-ebc8b3b3c698|https://www.loom.com/embed/7fa7364ac5814377bf339d2ce31ae2a5?sid=4e385c77-5ea4-4c1d-adda-ebc8b3b3c698|smart-embed]
In this video, well show you how to use Atlassian Intelligence in Jira to identify risks, automate work, and keep projects on track. See how AI can help you remove blockers before they slow you down and tickets with clear descriptions and acceptance criteria.
*Resources:*
* [Atlassian Intelligence overview|https://support.atlassian.com/organization-administration/docs/get-started-with-atlassian-intelligence-guide/] * [Use AI to write or create content|https://support.atlassian.com/jira-software-cloud/docs/use-atlassian-intelligence-to-help-write-or-edit-content/] * [Use AI to build better search queries|https://support.atlassian.com/jira-software-cloud/docs/use-atlassian-intelligence-to-search-for-issues/] * [How AI can create better automations|https://support.atlassian.com/cloud-automation/docs/use-atlassian-intelligence-with-jira-automation/]

Issue.creator: 9ea987f4-57dd-49c9-b17d-0a433b7c525f
Issue.summary: Security & permissions: How to control who can edit or or manage projects
Issue.description:
[https://www.loom.com/embed/b387523478a3417da222bc69403db9c0?sid=9c5cd990-e88a-41ca-b1c7-4f5fbe8ceb31|https://www.loom.com/embed/b387523478a3417da222bc69403db9c0?sid=9c5cd990-e88a-41ca-b1c7-4f5fbe8ceb31|smart-embed]
In this video, well show you how to control who can create, edit, or change project settings in Jira. Learn how to customize permissions so the right people have the right access, so your projects are secure and organized.
*Resources:*
* [Permissions overview|https://www.atlassian.com/software/jira/guides/permissions/overview] * [How to change permissions|https://www.atlassian.com/software/jira/guides/permissions/tutorials] * [Manage project permissions|https://support.atlassian.com/jira-cloud-administration/docs/manage-project-permissions/]

Issue.creator: 9ea987f4-57dd-49c9-b17d-0a433b7c525f
Issue.summary: Plans: How to use detailed roadmaps to plan out your work
Issue.description:
[https://www.loom.com/embed/88f966bbfc434507b26c397ab0923f3e?sid=3db973df-3c55-4045-a363-12053db42c32|https://www.loom.com/embed/88f966bbfc434507b26c397ab0923f3e?sid=3db973df-3c55-4045-a363-12053db42c32|smart-embed]
In this video, well show you how to use Plans to plan your work, track dependencies, and keep teams aligned. Learn how to build roadmaps into your teams rituals and manage work so you always deliver on time.
*Resources:*
* [Plans overview|https://www.atlassian.com/software/jira/guides/advanced-roadmaps/overview] * [Getting started with Plans|https://support.atlassian.com/jira-software-cloud/docs/get-started-with-advanced-roadmaps/] * [More video tutorials on how to create a Plan|https://www.atlassian.com/software/jira/guides/advanced-roadmaps/tutorials]

Status.name: Building
Status.description: Source code has been committed, and JIRA is waiting for the code to be built before moving to the next status.

Status.name: Open
Status.description: The work item is open and ready for the assignee to start work on it.

Status.name: In Progress
Status.description: This work item is being actively worked on at the moment by the assignee.

Status.name: Reopened
Status.description: This work item was once resolved, but the resolution was deemed incorrect. From here the work items are either reopened, or are closed.

Status.name: Resolved
Status.description: A resolution has been taken, and it's awaiting verification by the reporter. From here work items are either reopened, or are closed.

Status.name: Closed
Status.description: The work item is considered finished, the resolution is correct. work items which are closed can be reopened.

Status.name: Build Broken
Status.description: The source code committed for this work item has possibly broken the build.
